s relatifs, les donn&eacute;es peuvent &ecirc;tre conserv&eacute;es au maximum pour une dur&eacute;e de trois ans.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cpartie r&eacute;alise aussi d&rsquo;autres traitements de donn&eacute;es pour d&rsquo;autres finalit&eacute;s que la stricte ex&eacute;cution d&rsquo;une adh&eacute;sion. N&eacute;anmoins ces traitements feront l&rsquo;objet de votre consentement, que vous pourrez retirer &agrave; tout moment. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A cet effet, les finalit&eacute;s poursuivies par Cpartie sont les suivantes: </span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\">\r\n		<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Assurer la s&eacute;curit&eacute; de la plateforme et des services</span>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\">\r\n		<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Am&eacute;liorer les offres et la relation client </span>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Cpartie traite &eacute;galement vos donn&eacute;es pour r&eacute;pondre &agrave; ses obligations l&eacute;gales ou r&egrave;glementaires.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">A cet effet, les finalit&eacute;s poursuivies par Cpartie sont les suivantes :</span>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\">\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\">\r\n		<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align: justify;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:40